            <p>You might need help or assistance regarding your needs of machines. Please contact us anytime at one of the methods below.</p>
            <div class="clear"></div>

            <ul class="list-inline list_btm">
                <li class="list-inline-item">
                    <div class="d-inline-block align-middle pr-2">
                        <img src="{{ app.request.baseurl }}/asset/images/icons_phone-bg.png" alt="" class="img img-fluid">
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-inline-block align-middle">
